# Form Attributes
1. Action - adding the server pages or url address or path (used when we dont use javascript)
2. Method -
get = Data is visible in url address
post = Hides the data
3. enctype= encryption type
 - application/x-www-form-urlencoded - default type
 - multipart/form data= file upload(used)
 4. autocomplete = 
 - browser history (form history)
 @ on = enables the autofill
 @ off = disables the autofill

## Form Tags:
1. fieldset = Draws a border line around the form area
2. legend = Title of the form
3. input =  user inputs 
- attributes:
  @ type attribute : decides the input type
  @ name attribute = field name(unique)
  @ id - field id(unique)
  @ placeholder - hint for the user // not applicable for select
  @ Required - Mandatory 
  @ readonly - disables the write property/operation
  @ value - default value
  
4. label = form  input label-----usually used to give user input
5. select = dropdown 
6. textarea = multiline text input


